WEBVTT

01:43.070 --> 01:45.950
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.060
[Episode 12]

01:53.390 --> 01:54.190
Yan.

01:55.030 --> 01:56.080
Yan!

01:56.270 --> 01:57.110
Yan.

01:59.370 --> 02:00.330
Qianqian!

02:05.960 --> 02:07.020
Yan…

02:09.070 --> 02:09.949
Help me.

02:10.830 --> 02:12.190
Yan, help me.

02:12.590 --> 02:13.270
Man.

02:13.310 --> 02:13.990
Man.

02:14.020 --> 02:15.190
Yan, help me.

02:17.000 --> 02:18.930
Yan, why didn't you save me?

02:19.630 --> 02:21.470
Yan, why didn't you save me?

02:21.950 --> 02:23.870
Why didn't you save me?

02:24.790 --> 02:25.670
Yan, help me.

02:25.750 --> 02:26.870
Yan, why didn't you save me?

02:26.910 --> 02:28.829
Yan, why didn't you save me?

02:29.550 --> 02:30.910
Yan, why didn't you save me?

02:30.990 --> 02:32.590
Yan, why didn't you save me?

03:16.500 --> 03:17.130
Look.

03:17.270 --> 03:18.300
This is for you.

03:18.310 --> 03:19.220
Is it nice?

03:19.750 --> 03:20.780
I made it myself.

03:23.640 --> 03:24.570
One for each of us.

03:24.670 --> 03:25.340
What do you think?

03:25.820 --> 03:26.450
Is it shiny?

03:26.710 --> 03:27.890
There's a heart, too.

03:44.480 --> 03:46.000
What's wrong?

03:46.610 --> 03:48.140
Are you unhappy recently?

03:50.829 --> 03:51.740
I...

03:54.630 --> 03:55.960
I like Jiang Chengyi.

04:02.670 --> 04:04.140
You...

04:04.470 --> 04:06.110
What are you talking about?

04:08.530 --> 04:09.790
I like Jiang Chengyi.

04:12.720 --> 04:13.500
Yan!

04:19.860 --> 04:20.690
Man.

04:25.490 --> 04:27.100
You're my best friend.

04:28.360 --> 04:30.080
You are very important

04:31.150 --> 04:32.480
in my heart.

04:34.030 --> 04:35.310
I won't be mad at you

04:35.350 --> 04:36.470
because I know you can't control

04:36.490 --> 04:37.690
the feeling of "liking."

04:39.760 --> 04:40.940
Can you

04:41.230 --> 04:42.560
give me a chance?

04:44.940 --> 04:45.730
What...

04:46.040 --> 04:47.890
What chance can I give you?

04:49.170 --> 04:50.370
Can you

04:51.000 --> 04:52.820
break up with Jiang Chengyi?

04:53.790 --> 04:54.670
Just one month.

04:55.540 --> 04:58.000
Even a week

04:58.600 --> 04:59.500
will do.

04:59.940 --> 05:01.390
Just consider it helping me.

05:11.990 --> 05:14.070
Aren't you my best friend?

05:17.680 --> 05:18.740
You are my best friend.

05:18.790 --> 05:20.880
Why don't you help me?

05:21.060 --> 05:23.230
I can't…

05:23.270 --> 05:24.510
I can't even breathe.

05:24.590 --> 05:26.190
I'm dying!

05:28.390 --> 05:29.190
Man.

05:32.590 --> 05:33.610
Calm down.

05:33.630 --> 05:35.040
I can't.

05:35.270 --> 05:36.480
I can't.

05:37.310 --> 05:38.000
Yan.

05:38.020 --> 05:39.200
I beg you.

05:43.430 --> 05:44.050
Fine.

05:45.220 --> 05:46.870
If you really like him that much,

05:46.890 --> 05:48.580
tell him yourself.

05:49.300 --> 05:50.230
If we are

05:50.230 --> 05:51.310
to fight for him,

05:52.840 --> 05:54.350
it'll be unfair to him.

05:59.400 --> 06:00.820
I won't break up with him,

06:03.830 --> 06:04.800
unless he...

06:06.150 --> 06:07.750
unless he's willing to break up with me

06:07.790 --> 06:09.390
and be with you.

06:16.870 --> 06:18.750
You don't want to help me?

06:22.620 --> 06:24.510
You don't want to help me?

06:28.700 --> 06:29.430
I...

06:32.350 --> 06:32.990
I...

07:18.300 --> 07:22.820
[May you get everything you desire, and may what you get be the best]

07:18.300 --> 07:22.820
[May you live a courageous life, daring to love, to hate, and to chase your dreams. May you live with an open heart]

07:28.300 --> 07:30.510
[You ruined my life]

07:33.450 --> 07:34.500
Man,

07:35.110 --> 07:35.480
[I hate you]

07:35.510 --> 07:36.510
I know you will never

07:36.550 --> 07:37.710
forgive me.

07:38.750 --> 07:40.150
You shouldn't forgive me, either.

07:42.180 --> 07:43.330
You're dead.

07:43.640 --> 07:44.590
Qianqian is dead.

07:46.140 --> 07:47.810
It's all because

07:48.530 --> 07:49.890
I couldn't hold you back in the end.

07:57.750 --> 08:01.150
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

08:07.160 --> 08:11.440
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

08:13.560 --> 08:14.260
How is it?

08:15.840 --> 08:18.130
[Surveillance Network Coverage Areas, Anshan District, Ninghai]

08:16.380 --> 08:17.530
Not so good.

08:17.830 --> 08:19.390
We checked all the vehicles

08:19.430 --> 08:20.110
which had gone into or out of the alley.

08:21.560 --> 08:22.470
You didn't find her?

08:22.860 --> 08:23.960
We've checked all. No.

08:24.070 --> 08:25.210
How is that possible?

08:26.060 --> 08:26.910
I've checked all the CCTV

08:26.950 --> 08:28.280
of the people who had gone past the intersection.

08:28.390 --> 08:29.160
Since Wang Qianqian

08:29.190 --> 08:30.030
went into that alley,

08:30.070 --> 08:31.070
she never came out.

08:34.559 --> 08:36.020
Let me check the CCTV again.

08:36.860 --> 08:39.950
[Surveillance Network Coverage Areas, Anshan District, Ninghai]

08:44.900 --> 08:45.830
Have you recorded all the vehicles

08:45.850 --> 08:46.410
going in and out?

08:46.680 --> 08:47.360
Yes.

08:47.530 --> 08:49.550
I even checked all the motorcycles and tricycles.

08:49.910 --> 08:51.570
Then, how did she get out?

09:11.250 --> 09:12.920
Could it be this thing?

09:13.830 --> 09:14.830
The trash can?

09:15.400 --> 09:17.180
Considering Wang Qianqian's figure,

09:17.410 --> 09:18.920
the trash can is big enough to hold her.

09:23.300 --> 09:24.300
Contact

09:24.320 --> 09:25.390
the garbage collector that day.

09:25.420 --> 09:26.450
I'll go there with Qin Yue.

09:27.870 --> 09:29.200
You two stay here.

09:29.220 --> 09:29.820
Okay.

09:32.360 --> 09:34.680
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

09:37.650 --> 09:38.250
Hello?

09:39.350 --> 09:40.230
Chengyi,

09:40.700 --> 09:42.060
you finally picked up.

09:42.190 --> 09:43.680
What are you and Lu Yan busy with?

09:44.040 --> 09:45.680
Yeah, Captain Jiang,

09:45.710 --> 09:46.350
where have you

09:46.350 --> 09:47.360
taken Lu Yan?

09:47.390 --> 09:48.070
She doesn't answer our calls

09:48.110 --> 09:49.080
or reply to our messages.

09:49.110 --> 09:49.790
What are you doing?

09:50.750 --> 09:52.480
Something happened to her friend.

09:52.510 --> 09:53.850
She might be in a bad mood.

09:53.990 --> 09:54.720
What?

09:54.870 --> 09:55.790
Lu Yan's in trouble?

09:55.810 --> 09:56.470
What?

09:56.600 --> 09:57.880
Lu Yan's in trouble?

09:57.910 --> 09:58.820
It's not her.

09:59.230 --> 10:00.230
It's Wang Qianqian.

10:00.890 --> 10:02.260
We're still investigating.

10:02.280 --> 10:03.380
I can't say more.

10:05.880 --> 10:07.000
Wang Qianqian?

10:07.390 --> 10:07.870
Wait...

10:09.000 --> 10:10.070
My goodness.

10:10.310 --> 10:11.440
No wonder her sister

10:11.470 --> 10:12.150
asked me for leave

10:12.150 --> 10:13.570
to handle a family matter.

10:13.910 --> 10:15.310
She hasn't come to work for days.

10:15.720 --> 10:18.510
If you can't reach Yan,

10:18.910 --> 10:20.220
go to her home.

10:20.870 --> 10:21.680
Try to...

10:22.710 --> 10:23.770
console her.

10:24.140 --> 10:24.890
Alright.

10:25.290 --> 10:26.580
Lu Yan, don't worry.

10:26.710 --> 10:27.790
I'll go to her home now.

10:27.870 --> 10:28.680
If her condition is not good,

10:28.710 --> 10:29.670
I'll stay there.

10:29.760 --> 10:30.840
Just focus on your investigation.

10:31.830 --> 10:32.440
Okay.

10:32.850 --> 10:34.250
I'm hanging up. I'm going to work.

10:39.400 --> 10:40.520
Where are you going?

10:40.550 --> 10:41.630
I'm packing up for you.

10:44.940 --> 10:45.770
Oh my god.

11:38.310 --> 11:39.430
Sorry, Lu Yan.

11:40.210 --> 11:41.210
I'm late.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.940
I should've come earlier.

11:59.620 --> 12:00.750
Last night,

12:00.790 --> 12:02.510
I had a nightmare.

12:03.070 --> 12:05.180
I don't know who it was.

12:05.310 --> 12:07.150
I thought it was Qianqian.

12:09.990 --> 12:11.430
So, I swam desperately.

12:11.450 --> 12:12.700
So desperately.

12:12.870 --> 12:13.650
I thought

12:13.680 --> 12:15.850
if I could hold her back,

12:16.270 --> 12:17.870
she would come back.

12:20.210 --> 12:22.140
But when I approached her,

12:22.160 --> 12:23.840
I found she was Man.

12:23.860 --> 12:25.470
I dreamed of Man again.

12:25.470 --> 12:27.480
I don't want to be like this anymore.

12:27.510 --> 12:28.390
You know?

12:28.430 --> 12:29.630
I feel

12:29.790 --> 12:30.490
I...

12:30.590 --> 12:32.150
I'm going crazy.

12:33.390 --> 12:35.990
I don't know what to do.

12:41.800 --> 12:42.740
Lu Yan.

12:42.880 --> 12:43.850
Listen to me.

12:44.350 --> 12:45.510
You can't blame all the mistakes

12:45.550 --> 12:46.670
on yourself.

12:46.690 --> 12:47.490
Understand?

12:49.060 --> 12:50.850
You'll drive yourself crazy.

12:54.810 --> 12:56.070
If...

12:57.970 --> 12:59.500
If I had agreed

13:00.580 --> 13:02.200
to Man back then…

13:03.540 --> 13:04.550
If...

13:06.110 --> 13:08.140
If

13:08.290 --> 13:10.940
I had received Qianqian's call,

13:11.550 --> 13:13.270
I don't know if they

13:13.300 --> 13:15.350
would still be alive now.

13:21.880 --> 13:23.120
It's not your fault.

13:24.350 --> 13:25.990
Don't push yourself to the dead end.

13:28.990 --> 13:30.000
Take your time.

13:30.350 --> 13:31.370
It's okay.

13:32.920 --> 13:34.450
Everything will pass.

13:35.020 --> 13:36.060
Everything will be fine.

13:39.390 --> 13:40.860
Can you give me a hug?

13:56.940 --> 14:01.040
[Trash Collection and Temporary Storage Point]

13:58.930 --> 13:59.770
Well,

13:59.890 --> 14:00.750
when was the trash can

14:00.750 --> 14:01.310
lost?

14:01.590 --> 14:02.680
Two days ago.

14:02.750 --> 14:03.520
When I came in the morning,

14:03.550 --> 14:04.310
it was gone.

14:04.910 --> 14:06.230
It's pretty rough around here.

14:06.350 --> 14:07.260
We thought

14:07.280 --> 14:09.230
someone must have taken it.

14:09.460 --> 14:10.600
It's not valuable,

14:10.630 --> 14:11.990
so we didn't call the police.

14:16.720 --> 14:17.490
Is this it?

14:20.440 --> 14:25.250
[Trash Collection and Temporary Storage Point]

14:20.600 --> 14:21.440
Yes.

14:21.460 --> 14:22.940
But that uniform is not ours.

14:23.030 --> 14:24.080
Our company's uniform

14:24.140 --> 14:25.470
has the company name on it.

14:29.910 --> 14:30.440
Okay, thank you.

14:30.470 --> 14:31.150
Sorry for the trouble.

14:31.170 --> 14:31.970
You're welcome.

15:14.550 --> 15:15.720
[Trash Collection Point 2]

15:34.270 --> 15:35.630
If this is the case,

15:36.300 --> 15:37.150
the suspect must have put

15:37.190 --> 15:38.790
Wang Qianqian

15:38.810 --> 15:40.110
into the trash can,

15:40.510 --> 15:41.740
pushed it out of this area,

15:42.230 --> 15:43.600
put her in a vehicle,

15:43.790 --> 15:45.420
and driven to Chanson Artificial Lake

15:45.600 --> 15:46.360
to dump the body.

15:46.910 --> 15:47.750
If that's the case,

15:47.750 --> 15:49.170
there's a deserted lake five kilometers away.

15:49.230 --> 15:50.410
Isn't it more convenient to dump it there?

15:50.830 --> 15:52.340
I also find it strange.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.930
It was over 20 kilometers.

15:54.430 --> 15:55.550
If he'd been stopped

15:55.590 --> 15:57.230
for a random inspection on the way,

15:57.950 --> 15:58.710
he'd be exposed.

16:00.310 --> 16:01.000
Why?

16:06.460 --> 16:09.950
[Public Security]

16:12.740 --> 16:13.370
Liu Hao.

16:14.000 --> 16:14.690
Have you found anything?

16:15.350 --> 16:16.070
No.

16:16.390 --> 16:17.700
The latest suspect was that three years ago,

16:17.720 --> 16:18.790
in the village

16:18.790 --> 16:19.430
to the south of the artificial lake,

16:19.500 --> 16:20.490
there was a murder before.

16:21.190 --> 16:22.330
But the murderer

16:22.360 --> 16:23.320
has already been sentenced.

16:23.350 --> 16:24.360
He's in jail now.

16:36.700 --> 16:37.420
Hello?

16:37.740 --> 16:39.410
[Jiang]

16:38.400 --> 16:39.300
Captain Jiang.

16:39.490 --> 16:40.190
I'm calling to tell you

16:40.230 --> 16:40.950
about Lu Yan's situation.

16:41.640 --> 16:42.400
Go ahead.

16:43.280 --> 16:44.600
She's better today.

16:44.730 --> 16:45.680
I asked her to go out

16:45.710 --> 16:46.620
for a walk to relax.

16:46.740 --> 16:47.910
She didn't ask me to accompany her,

16:48.290 --> 16:50.100
but I think it should be fine.

16:50.780 --> 16:51.510
Last night,

16:51.550 --> 16:52.710
we chatted for a long time.

16:53.270 --> 16:53.750
Her situation

16:53.750 --> 16:55.120
is a little tricky now.

16:55.140 --> 16:56.580
Wang Qianqian and Deng Man

16:56.590 --> 16:57.590
both drowned,

16:57.760 --> 16:59.410
and she thinks she's responsible for both,

16:59.670 --> 17:01.100
so she has mixed them up.

17:03.440 --> 17:04.490
Also,

17:04.589 --> 17:05.190
they both happened

17:05.210 --> 17:06.200
when she was with you.

17:08.369 --> 17:09.109
I see.

17:09.740 --> 17:10.630
You...

17:11.690 --> 17:12.650
try to comfort her, okay?

17:12.869 --> 17:13.640
I'm hanging up.

17:17.260 --> 17:18.079
Liu Hao.

17:18.180 --> 17:21.140
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

17:18.910 --> 17:19.880
Check something out.

17:20.329 --> 17:23.010
Eight years ago,

17:23.160 --> 17:23.750
a girl named Deng Man

17:24.520 --> 17:25.690
committed suicide.

17:25.980 --> 17:26.560
Find out

17:26.589 --> 17:28.030
where it happened.

17:28.790 --> 17:29.680
Eight years ago?

17:29.790 --> 17:30.310
Okay.

17:41.540 --> 17:42.180
Got it.

17:42.560 --> 17:43.390
The victim, Deng Man,

17:43.720 --> 17:45.900
drowned in a wildlife pond in the western suburbs.

17:46.470 --> 17:47.810
The wildlife pond in the western suburbs?

17:48.460 --> 17:49.220
That is exactly

17:49.240 --> 17:50.630
the current Chanson Artificial Lake.

17:51.700 --> 17:52.690
It is here, right?

17:52.840 --> 17:53.360
Yes.

17:55.800 --> 17:59.390
[Social Relationship] [Premeditated murder]

18:01.910 --> 18:02.430
Senior.

18:02.500 --> 18:03.120
Hao.

18:06.830 --> 18:08.730
I just finished comparing them.

18:10.270 --> 18:11.920
We can't be sure

18:11.950 --> 18:13.070
if they're the same person, but

18:13.870 --> 18:15.930
their height and posture are very similar.

18:16.650 --> 18:17.410
Right?

18:19.240 --> 18:20.720
This is coming for Lu Yan.

18:23.050 --> 18:23.860
Lu Yan?

18:25.420 --> 18:27.130
Professor Yu is right.

18:27.410 --> 18:28.850
The behavior and motive

18:29.750 --> 18:30.760
of this case's suspect

18:30.790 --> 18:31.430
are strange,

18:31.560 --> 18:32.120
so we've been

18:32.150 --> 18:33.030
unable to make any headway.

18:33.980 --> 18:35.540
If he just wanted to

18:35.590 --> 18:36.970
kill Wang Qianqian,

18:37.090 --> 18:38.320
he could have

18:38.350 --> 18:38.870
done it

18:38.870 --> 18:40.160
where there was no surveillance.

18:40.860 --> 18:42.580
Not only did he not do it,

18:42.630 --> 18:43.510
but he also

18:43.530 --> 18:44.420
transported Wang Qianqian out

18:44.550 --> 18:45.260
after drugging her into unconsciousness

18:45.290 --> 18:46.800
He even transported her to the Chanson Artificial Lake

18:46.830 --> 18:48.010
20 kilometers away

18:48.190 --> 18:48.740
to make her

18:48.770 --> 18:49.840
drown there.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.630
He needed to pass through the city center

18:51.710 --> 18:52.970
on this trip.

18:52.990 --> 18:53.790
To travel so far

18:53.810 --> 18:55.110
is quite risky for him.

18:55.400 --> 18:56.580
Why did he do that?

18:57.010 --> 18:57.940
Unless that lake

18:57.970 --> 18:59.090
meant something special to him.

19:00.370 --> 19:01.150
Captain Jiang,

19:01.420 --> 19:02.430
you mean

19:02.460 --> 19:03.300
the murderer

19:03.330 --> 19:04.050
wanted them

19:04.080 --> 19:05.050
to die in one place?

19:05.830 --> 19:07.080
I think it's possible.

19:08.190 --> 19:09.800
Could it be a coincidence?

19:11.510 --> 19:12.780
If two people

19:12.830 --> 19:14.820
died in one place,

19:15.650 --> 19:17.110
it could be a coincidence.

19:17.140 --> 19:18.230
But our case

19:18.270 --> 19:18.860
is different.

19:19.310 --> 19:21.290
There are many questionable points about it.

19:22.420 --> 19:23.770
So, you mean

19:23.810 --> 19:24.760
the murderer

19:24.790 --> 19:27.150
wanted the body to be found?

19:29.230 --> 19:30.550
He didn't just want us

19:30.590 --> 19:31.670
to find the body.

19:33.550 --> 19:35.570
On the night Wang Qianqian was killed,

19:35.660 --> 19:37.580
she called Lu Yan

19:38.060 --> 19:39.620
at 10 p.m.,

19:40.310 --> 19:41.840
but Lu Yan didn't receive it.

19:42.530 --> 19:43.860
She also sent a message

19:44.010 --> 19:45.680
at 11:14 p.m.

19:46.100 --> 19:47.920
However, according to

19:47.960 --> 19:49.590
the forensic report,

19:50.190 --> 19:51.270
at 11:14,

19:51.290 --> 19:53.140
Wang Qianqian was probably already dead.

19:54.410 --> 19:55.670
It's impossible for her to send the message at that moment.

19:56.390 --> 19:57.930
If the murderer

19:57.950 --> 19:59.270
sent the message himself,

19:59.420 --> 20:00.570
why did he do that?

20:00.990 --> 20:02.470
I didn't understand at first,

20:03.940 --> 20:05.080
but then I saw

20:05.110 --> 20:06.190
your photo comparison.

20:10.070 --> 20:11.170
If the person

20:11.560 --> 20:13.390
disguising as Deng Man

20:13.590 --> 20:15.260
and the person who killed Wang Qianqian

20:15.290 --> 20:16.780
are the same person,

20:18.160 --> 20:19.790
then his motive is clear.

20:19.950 --> 20:21.330
He wants to drag Lu Yan

20:22.180 --> 20:23.030
back into

20:23.070 --> 20:24.310
her misery eight years ago.

20:25.300 --> 20:26.540
So, he did it to retaliate against Lu Yan

20:26.590 --> 20:27.550
for Deng Man?

20:29.220 --> 20:30.330
Is there any other possibility?

20:31.590 --> 20:33.010
This is also just speculation.

20:33.270 --> 20:34.890
We still need to find clues.

20:38.530 --> 20:39.870
Since these two cases

20:39.910 --> 20:40.750
are so related,

20:40.770 --> 20:42.200
can we

20:42.240 --> 20:43.190
ask Dr. Lu

20:43.190 --> 20:44.150
to get more information about the situation?

20:45.800 --> 20:46.660
Don't go to her just yet.

20:48.340 --> 20:50.160
Deng Man's case

20:50.250 --> 20:51.740
was closed by suicide.

20:51.760 --> 20:53.730
Before we have solid evidence,

20:53.750 --> 20:54.900
we can't merge the cases.

20:55.390 --> 20:56.280
Let's straighten out

20:56.310 --> 20:57.670
the clues we have.

21:02.650 --> 21:05.900
[Shoe prints at the scene] [Abandon the body after anesthesia]

21:10.420 --> 21:11.440
I have to go out for a bit.

21:20.150 --> 21:20.750
Tang Jie,

21:20.770 --> 21:22.070
where is Lu Yan now?

21:22.150 --> 21:23.680
She should be at the Seaside Park,

21:23.710 --> 21:25.030
where she usually runs.

21:25.290 --> 21:26.230
Okay, I got it.

21:50.270 --> 21:51.960
No, hurry up.

21:52.640 --> 21:54.010
I can't run anymore.

21:54.230 --> 21:54.790
No.

21:54.810 --> 21:55.270
No.

21:55.310 --> 21:56.340
Then, let me

21:56.340 --> 21:57.300
rest for a while.

21:57.430 --> 21:57.910
No.

21:58.000 --> 21:59.470
Just ten minutes.

21:59.550 --> 22:00.190
Six minutes.

22:00.870 --> 22:02.030
No, five minutes.

22:02.030 --> 22:03.670
I'll recite it for you now.

22:04.830 --> 22:07.140
The typical symptoms of mechanical bowel obstruction

22:07.170 --> 22:10.590
are abdominal pain

22:11.510 --> 22:12.390
and… and…

22:12.550 --> 22:13.310
vomiting.

22:13.350 --> 22:13.960
Wrong.

22:14.370 --> 22:15.190
But that is it.

22:15.190 --> 22:16.290
If I say it's wrong, it's wrong.

22:16.550 --> 22:18.860
Mechanical… Abdominal pain,

22:19.120 --> 22:20.030
vomiting…

22:20.470 --> 22:21.710
And what else?

22:21.790 --> 22:22.640
Diarrhea?

22:22.860 --> 22:23.600
Wrong.

22:24.110 --> 22:24.990
Give me some water.

22:24.990 --> 22:26.290
You're driving me crazy. Hurry up.

22:26.430 --> 22:27.740
You don't buy water

22:27.790 --> 22:28.310
but drink mine every day.

22:29.030 --> 22:30.680
Why didn't you buy me a bottle?

22:30.710 --> 22:31.550
Here.

22:40.130 --> 22:40.710
No.

22:40.730 --> 22:42.120
I'm really going to die

22:42.150 --> 22:43.390
if you keep running,

22:44.220 --> 22:44.630
Let's go.

22:44.660 --> 22:45.270
Go!

22:45.630 --> 22:46.590
No!

22:47.230 --> 22:48.620
I'm exhausted!

23:36.400 --> 23:37.070
Zhong,

23:38.230 --> 23:39.250
do me a favor.

23:47.380 --> 23:50.270
[Huiting Complex]

24:01.110 --> 24:01.870
Tang Jie,

24:04.250 --> 24:06.020
thank you for being with me these days.

24:08.150 --> 24:09.620
I should thank you.

24:09.810 --> 24:11.860
Otherwise, Zhong always snores when he sleeps.

24:11.960 --> 24:12.510
At your place,

24:12.510 --> 24:13.590
I can rest better.

24:18.880 --> 24:19.690
Tang Jie,

24:21.790 --> 24:22.930
tell me,

24:25.570 --> 24:26.470
how can I have

24:26.470 --> 24:27.880
such a good friend like you?

24:30.310 --> 24:31.880
You must have done good deeds

24:31.910 --> 24:33.550
in your previous life.

24:41.780 --> 24:42.640
Tang Jie.

24:47.750 --> 24:48.540
Everything

24:52.010 --> 24:53.350
will get better, right?

24:56.510 --> 24:57.310
Of course.

25:09.710 --> 25:10.590
Thank you.

25:33.870 --> 25:34.620
Yan.

25:49.600 --> 25:50.910
You are here, Yan.

25:51.500 --> 25:52.850
-Why are you up so early?
-You're up?

25:54.000 --> 25:54.990
I keep having nightmares.

25:54.990 --> 25:56.100
It is nice to just stay here

25:56.120 --> 25:56.610
and enjoy the scenery.

25:56.750 --> 25:57.150
Look.

25:59.850 --> 26:00.880
It's okay.

26:01.030 --> 26:03.180
Dreams are the opposite of reality.

26:05.520 --> 26:06.440
Are you

26:06.470 --> 26:07.260
going to

26:07.310 --> 26:08.910
a dental meeting today?

26:08.940 --> 26:10.440
I heard you mention it on the phone yesterday.

26:10.910 --> 26:12.190
I turned it down.

26:13.670 --> 26:15.110
I'm fine.

26:15.130 --> 26:16.330
Don't worry.

26:17.610 --> 26:18.350
Really?

26:18.430 --> 26:19.230
Yes.

26:23.710 --> 26:24.810
It will pass.

26:25.200 --> 26:26.370
I will…

26:27.150 --> 26:28.260
pull myself together.

26:30.230 --> 26:31.700
You're saying it,

26:31.790 --> 26:33.480
but look at your dark circles.

26:35.260 --> 26:36.330
I...

26:36.820 --> 26:38.380
I was born this way.

26:39.320 --> 26:40.650
Don't worry.

26:45.340 --> 26:47.280
There has been clattering and banging the whole morning.

26:47.310 --> 26:48.110
I don't know what they're doing.

26:48.230 --> 26:49.230
It's very loud.

26:49.580 --> 26:51.320
A new neighbor is moving in, right?

26:51.590 --> 26:52.390
Moving in?

26:57.430 --> 26:59.040
I'll go check it out.

27:04.760 --> 27:05.620
Breakfast!

27:06.670 --> 27:07.340
Zhong?

27:07.380 --> 27:08.300
Honey?

27:09.150 --> 27:10.440
I bought breakfast for you two.

27:11.890 --> 27:12.400
Wait,

27:12.440 --> 27:13.300
did you hear

27:13.330 --> 27:14.670
a loud noise just now?

27:15.400 --> 27:16.330
I was in a hurry.

27:16.360 --> 27:17.940
I bumped into the door next door.

27:17.980 --> 27:19.390
Come on in.

27:19.660 --> 27:20.760
Let's go and eat first.

27:20.790 --> 27:21.900
Your husband is drunk again.

27:21.920 --> 27:23.130
He even hit the door.

27:26.130 --> 27:26.790
Honey.

27:26.810 --> 27:28.080
Please put them on the plates.

27:32.400 --> 27:34.320
Why did you buy so much stuff?

27:34.360 --> 27:36.190
You've bought everything at the breakfast stall, haven't you?

27:36.230 --> 27:37.030
Yeah.

27:37.060 --> 27:38.260
Thank you, Zhong.

27:38.910 --> 27:39.980
For what?

27:40.190 --> 27:41.330
I bought it for my wife,

27:41.360 --> 27:42.660
and I picked up a little something for you as well.

27:42.700 --> 27:44.080
These are eggs,

27:44.370 --> 27:45.670
soy milk,

27:45.700 --> 27:46.870
glutinous rice balls,

27:46.900 --> 27:47.680
scallion pancakes,

27:47.700 --> 27:49.180
and Yangchun Noodles.

27:49.910 --> 27:50.680
Is that enough, honey?

27:50.700 --> 27:51.540
Enough.

27:51.740 --> 27:53.270
It's too much.

27:53.500 --> 27:54.410
After we finish,

27:54.430 --> 27:55.650
you can take your wife

27:55.670 --> 27:56.350
back.

27:57.430 --> 27:58.710
Don't act tough.

27:59.590 --> 28:00.700
I'm not acting tough.

28:00.790 --> 28:02.140
I'm fine, really.

28:02.420 --> 28:03.160
Eat up.

28:03.670 --> 28:04.460
Let's eat first.

28:07.430 --> 28:08.040
Yummy.

28:10.990 --> 28:11.750
I've got a pair already.

28:11.750 --> 28:12.300
Use them yourself.

28:16.620 --> 28:17.820
It's great to have you two.

28:34.620 --> 28:35.550
Destroy.

28:35.030 --> 28:36.410
♫The day♫

28:36.000 --> 28:36.940
Rebuild.

28:37.510 --> 28:40.330
♫You barged into my world♫

28:37.520 --> 28:39.060
Life pushed me

28:39.080 --> 28:40.610
to the darkest moment again and again.

28:41.620 --> 28:43.210
♫I knew there wouldn't be♫

28:42.400 --> 28:43.390
It seems that I'm used to

28:43.430 --> 28:44.780
this kind of helplessness

28:43.930 --> 28:47.330
♫Anyone better than you♫

28:45.420 --> 28:46.710
and used to

28:46.910 --> 28:48.190
constantly healing myself.

28:49.710 --> 28:51.770
"Being used to it."

28:50.260 --> 28:51.950
♫Too bad♫

28:52.150 --> 28:53.420
It really hurts.

28:53.510 --> 28:55.970
♫I have no right to desire in my life♫

28:53.980 --> 28:55.700
I have no right to be pitied

28:56.710 --> 28:58.140
or to be sad.

28:56.800 --> 28:58.600
♫I missed my chance with you♫

28:59.560 --> 29:00.640
Maybe

28:59.820 --> 29:02.920
♫Can we blame it on fate?♫

29:01.080 --> 29:03.100
only by experiencing pain repeatedly

29:03.850 --> 29:05.160
can people grow up.

29:04.480 --> 29:07.620
[Recent 7890] [In memory of yesterday]

29:04.720 --> 29:07.740
♫Love songs always warn us♫

29:06.560 --> 29:08.330
Only by living on with scars

29:08.600 --> 29:11.590
♫Never to believe in forever and ever♫

29:09.510 --> 29:10.750
can we go further.

29:13.360 --> 29:16.500
♫I always go all out; my naivety's to blame♫

29:16.990 --> 29:20.540
♫Bear the pain and heartache♫

29:21.080 --> 29:23.890
♫Your kiss is♫

29:25.270 --> 29:30.260
♫Indelibly tattooed in my heart♫

29:30.990 --> 29:35.090
♫Believing in the rekindling of love♫

29:36.120 --> 29:39.430
♫You're closer than family♫

29:40.090 --> 29:43.500
♫Yet more unfamiliar than strangers♫

29:44.320 --> 29:47.810
♫Risking it all, only to be reciprocated with cruelty♫

29:48.890 --> 29:51.060
♫Aren't I stupid?♫

29:52.000 --> 29:55.260
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

29:56.220 --> 29:59.760
♫Must I give up my soul?♫

30:00.610 --> 30:07.310
♫I can never love anyone else again♫

30:17.810 --> 30:18.680
I didn't know

30:18.710 --> 30:20.400
there was such a beautiful boulevard

30:20.790 --> 30:21.870
near the hospital.

30:23.700 --> 30:24.970
Matron Qiao.

30:25.830 --> 30:26.860
Why are you here?

30:31.400 --> 30:33.150
Did something happen at the hospital?

30:33.910 --> 30:34.830
Everything is fine at the hospital.

30:49.460 --> 30:51.280
"One-Year Anniversary

30:51.630 --> 30:53.150
of Ms. Wang Qianqian

30:53.670 --> 30:54.630
as an Anesthesia Nurse."

30:57.060 --> 30:57.960
You wrote it, right?

31:03.360 --> 31:04.410
I found this

31:04.470 --> 31:06.150
while tidying Qianqian's cabinet.

31:08.320 --> 31:09.150
I think

31:10.760 --> 31:11.940
you should keep it.

31:18.380 --> 31:19.600
You know what?

31:21.290 --> 31:23.610
Before Qianqian was assigned to our department,

31:24.120 --> 31:25.900
the operating room wanted to keep her, too,

31:26.580 --> 31:27.710
but she insisted on

31:27.740 --> 31:29.260
becoming an anesthesia nurse.

31:30.390 --> 31:31.300
Do you know why?

31:38.960 --> 31:40.100
It was because of you.

31:51.220 --> 31:52.230
Matron Qiao.

31:53.480 --> 31:54.480
Matron Qiao.

31:54.790 --> 31:57.590
I want to stay in the anesthesiology department.

31:57.640 --> 31:58.490
Can I?

32:00.670 --> 32:01.780
Of course.

32:01.820 --> 32:02.530
But…

32:03.160 --> 32:05.720
I heard that Director Wang of the operating room

32:05.750 --> 32:06.790
wants you, too.

32:06.900 --> 32:08.190
Don't you want to think more about it?

32:10.700 --> 32:11.580
To be honest,

32:11.790 --> 32:12.910
nurses in the operating room

32:12.990 --> 32:14.240
have more opportunities to learn

32:14.790 --> 32:15.990
and more space to grow.

32:17.480 --> 32:18.860
I know,

32:19.270 --> 32:20.140
but

32:20.220 --> 32:21.000
I've thought about it

32:21.030 --> 32:21.790
very clearly.

32:24.320 --> 32:25.480
May I ask why?

32:31.680 --> 32:33.920
Because during my clinical rotations

32:33.960 --> 32:35.040
in the anesthesiology department,

32:35.140 --> 32:36.730
the people I've met the most

32:36.760 --> 32:38.690
were you and Dr. Lu.

32:39.270 --> 32:40.370
During those three months,

32:40.400 --> 32:41.420
Dr. Lu

32:41.430 --> 32:43.150
not only taught me

32:43.340 --> 32:44.430
how to manage postoperative care

32:44.480 --> 32:45.610
for patients

32:45.750 --> 32:46.630
but also taught me

32:46.650 --> 32:47.790
how to communicate with patients

32:47.870 --> 32:48.680
and comfort the patients.

32:49.250 --> 32:50.540
I always remember

32:50.590 --> 32:51.590
the thing she told me.

32:52.240 --> 32:53.020
She said

32:53.390 --> 32:54.390
without anesthesia,

32:54.420 --> 32:56.170
there wouldn't have been the development of surgeries.

32:56.340 --> 32:58.310
The greatest meaning of anesthesia

32:58.340 --> 32:59.750
is to do our best

32:59.830 --> 33:01.260
to reduce the pain of the patients

33:01.300 --> 33:03.470
so that we can cure more diseases.

33:04.040 --> 33:04.860
So...

33:05.150 --> 33:06.170
Matron Qiao,

33:06.380 --> 33:08.580
I want to be a member of

33:08.750 --> 33:10.430
the anesthesiology department like Dr. Lu.

33:12.280 --> 33:13.170
It was your words

33:14.270 --> 33:15.620
that made her find her direction.

33:18.170 --> 33:19.560
If you didn't tell me,

33:21.280 --> 33:22.480
I wouldn't know it.

33:26.130 --> 33:27.940
Even between best friends,

33:28.570 --> 33:30.320
there's still something you can't say to each other.

33:31.480 --> 33:32.190
Lu Yan,

33:34.290 --> 33:35.650
I'm telling you this today

33:35.710 --> 33:36.630
to tell you

33:37.130 --> 33:38.590
that I believe Qianqian

33:40.010 --> 33:41.510
would definitely not want to

33:41.890 --> 33:42.680
see you like this

33:42.710 --> 33:43.780
more than anyone else.

33:49.160 --> 33:49.920
Thank you.

33:55.230 --> 33:55.920
I'm leaving now.

34:05.560 --> 34:06.500
Dr. Lu.

34:08.960 --> 34:09.980
Come back early.

34:10.840 --> 34:11.590
We'll wait for you.

34:24.969 --> 34:31.550
[One-Year Anniversary of Ms. Wang Qianqian as an Anesthesia Nurse]

34:45.420 --> 34:49.420
[A small gift for the new neighbor]

34:54.730 --> 34:56.790
A small gift for the new neighbor.

35:26.350 --> 35:27.760
Since I was young,

35:27.970 --> 35:29.460
I've never done such heavy work.

35:29.490 --> 35:29.930
Yeah.

35:29.950 --> 35:30.390
Really,

35:30.410 --> 35:31.270
if it weren't for Jiang,

35:31.290 --> 35:31.860
I'm telling you…

35:33.290 --> 35:34.030
If it weren't for him,

35:34.070 --> 35:34.830
I wouldn't have done it, either.

35:36.550 --> 35:37.110
Leave it here.

35:37.140 --> 35:37.810
Okay.

35:38.300 --> 35:39.510
This place…

35:40.070 --> 35:40.870
is too small.

35:40.890 --> 35:41.730
Look at the dust.

35:41.960 --> 35:42.760
Let me tell you.

35:42.790 --> 35:43.960
The landlord has been abroad.

35:43.990 --> 35:45.340
This is just a storage room.

35:46.020 --> 35:47.190
It's too dusty.

35:47.220 --> 35:48.770
It's too dusty.

35:51.960 --> 35:52.800
What are you doing?

35:53.590 --> 35:54.500
What's wrong?

35:54.980 --> 35:56.480
You forgot who lives across the hall?

35:57.330 --> 35:57.960
Who?

35:58.180 --> 35:59.110
Are you stupid?

35:59.670 --> 36:00.240
Lu Yan!

36:07.630 --> 36:08.210
Zhong.

36:09.020 --> 36:10.880
Do we have to be like thieves?

36:11.050 --> 36:12.690
Don't we look like thieves now?

36:13.270 --> 36:14.350
Let's move things.

36:17.700 --> 36:18.630
Dalu.

36:18.650 --> 36:20.150
Did we look like thieves just now?

36:20.310 --> 36:21.430
Yes, Zhong.

36:24.650 --> 36:25.210
Zhong.

36:25.230 --> 36:26.000
What is this place?

36:26.020 --> 36:27.360
There's no water heater or gas stove.

36:27.390 --> 36:28.310
How can one live here?

36:28.330 --> 36:29.480
You're single for a reason.

36:29.870 --> 36:31.080
Is this for living?

36:31.100 --> 36:32.490
It's for love.

36:32.720 --> 36:34.440
I understand Jiang on this point.

36:34.590 --> 36:35.550
Okay. Okay.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.470
Teach me some moves.

36:38.500 --> 36:40.120
I'll go check it out.

36:40.780 --> 36:41.430
Hurry.

36:42.580 --> 36:44.300
Slowly.

36:46.540 --> 36:47.510
Breakfast!

38:14.560 --> 38:15.580
Hello?

38:26.560 --> 38:29.300
[Thank you for your little gift]

39:03.350 --> 39:05.640
[Thank you for your little gift]

39:06.200 --> 39:07.550
Thank you for your little gift.

40:06.430 --> 40:10.370
[News: A Woman Drowned in the Chanson Artificial Lake]

40:08.190 --> 40:08.670
Lately,

40:08.700 --> 40:09.830
a woman drowned

40:09.830 --> 40:11.190
in the Chanson Artificial Lake.

40:10.480 --> 40:12.460
[A Woman Drowned in the Chanson Artificial Lake]

40:18.790 --> 40:19.680
This lake...

40:21.510 --> 40:22.360
is the wildlife pond

40:22.400 --> 40:23.270
from ten years ago.
